data.name: txtParameters.ToolTip
data.value: font={fontname} // The font name to use size={int:0..100} // The font size (0=tiny, 100=enormous, 40-60=normal range) growth={float:0.25..4.0} // The factor to grow or shrink over time (0.5=shrink to half-size, 2.0=grow to double size) x={float:0..1} // The x-position of the center of the text (0.0=left side, 1.0=right side) y={float:0..1} // The y-position of the center of the text (0.0=top, 1.0=bottom) randx={float:0..1} // X-randomization: x will be bumped within +/- this value randy={float:0..1} // Y-randomization: y will be bumped within +/- this value time={float:0..999} // The duration (in seconds) the text will display fade={float:0..1} // The percentage of time (0..1) spent fading in the text ital={0|1} // Font italics override (0=off, 1=on) bold={0|1} // Font bold override (0=off, 1=on) r={int:0..255} // Red color component for the font g={int:0..255} // Green color component for the font b={int:0..255} // Blue color component for the font randr={int:0..255} // Randomization for the red component (r will be bumped within +/- this value) randg={int:0..255} // Randomization for the green component (g will be bumped within +/- this value) randb={int:0..255} // Randomization for the blue component (b will be bumped within +/- this value)
